Ask the user to enter a number 
Ask the user to enter another number
Ask the user to implement a operation between them
If the user chooses '+' then add the numbers
Display the answer
If the user chooses '-' then subtract the numbers
Display the answer and if the answer is smaller than 0 then display the '-' before the answer
If the user chooses '*' then multiply the numbers
Display the answer and if one of the numbers is negative then the answer will also be negative
If the user chooses '/' then divide the numbers
Display the answer and if the denominator is 0 then display error
